            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "@greyli you can't do a tuple as it returns a Response object, you get the error:\r\n`TypeError: <Response 35 bytes [200 OK]> is not JSON serializable`\r\n\r\n@davidism this produces manky code as you require three lines rather than one. This means that if you do full boundary checking, half your code base ends up mangling around this strange jsonify restriction. You can't even template it as it requires a request context."
