            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "A tuple works fine, the error indicates you're trying to jsonify a response, which is not what the example showed.\r\n\r\nWriting code is not a \"strange restriction\". If you want to modify a response, modify the response. If you want to change how responses are built to avoid repeating work, write a decorator or override `Flask.make_response`. If you want to pass data to a template as JSON, pass the data and use the `|tojson` filter."
